fields.detail:
Doing a general observation CCTV noticed that staff are not doing a proper bag search when entering and exciting the building.
 Its been noticed that some of the staff are only taking out a few of their contents from their bag, and then just opened that bag for the security look inside. Some of the staff are not even taking out any of their contents.

The security manager was informed and remind that there is a memo regarding this that staff should empty their entire content when entering or exciting the building.
